Package planning

Class TripPlanningMethods

java.lang.Object
planning.TripPlanningMethods
public class TripPlanningMethods extends Object
This class describes trip planning. It allows to calculate the best trip using bicycles from our model by entering: - The coordinates of the start of the trip - The coordinates of the end of the trip - The type of bicycle that we want to use (electrical or mechanical) There are different methods for this regarding the constraints added.
